{"tid":1380900,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"19DSE 報咗VTC 職專同學入","createTime":"2019-07-29T06:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T07:05:40.000Z","uid":252832,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"918fa68e7b09e09b0d41bdfc328695f931b7c47f","tid":1380900,"uid":252832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:25:15.000Z","msg":"我諗有唔少DSE 成績唔夠升HD，會選擇IVE 基礎文憑（DFS）或YC職專文憑（DVE）。<br />\n<br />\n不過有唔少同學都搞唔清兩者分別，簡單講，兩者都可以升讀IVE 開辦嘅高級文憑(HD)<br />\n<br />\n不過如果有意投考政府工嘅同學留意啦！<br />\n<br />\n只有，係只有完成基礎文憑（DFS）先會受公務員事務局承認你有等同5科2（包括中英文）嘅資歷。如果係炒數學嘅同學可以報埋「基礎數學（三）」補返個數學2。<br />\n<br />\n青年學院 DVE係無㗎<br />\n<br />\n如果中咗伏嘅同學，想轉讀返IVE，快啲打去問下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb36824a0e00369c3b2afcc64e3928d4cfee6eb","tid":1380900,"uid":225821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:29:20.000Z","msg":"報左邱子文，有咩需要注意？"},{"pid":"01d195be0938d8bc463f40ef30fd6cdccf7ddbe9","tid":1380900,"uid":252832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdb36824a0e00369c3b2afcc64e3928d4cfee6eb","tid":1380900,"uid":225821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:29:20.000Z","msg":"報左邱子文，有咩需要注意？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:41:16.000Z","msg":"睇入學須知，中六畢業生記得交第一期學費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遲交要收行政費㗎"},{"pid":"3ea848e5268db80bed87e83762e613853949252c","tid":1380900,"uid":225821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01d195be0938d8bc463f40ef30fd6cdccf7ddbe9","tid":1380900,"uid":252832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdb36824a0e00369c3b2afcc64e3928d4cfee6eb","tid":1380900,"uid":225821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:29:20.000Z","msg":"報左邱子文，有咩需要注意？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:41:16.000Z","msg":"睇入學須知，中六畢業生記得交第一期學費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遲交要收行政費㗎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:55: